track mouseDevTimecourse
superTrack on hide
shortLabel Bulk dev RNA-seq
longLabel Mouse developmental time course bulk RNA-seq
group regulation
html mouseDevTimecourse

    track developmentTimecourseM4mm10TPM
    parent mouseDevTimecourse
    type bigBarChart
    shortLabel timecourse M4 TPM
    longLabel Mouse development timecourse GENCODE M4 TPM
    visibility pack
    barChartUnit TPM
    barChartFacets tissue,timepoint
    barChartStretchToItem on
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/mm10/mouseDevTimecourse/mouse_development_TPM_M4_mm10.bb
    barChartCategoryUrl /gbdb/mm10/mouseDevTimecourse/mouse_development_M4.categories
    barChartStatsUrl /gbdb/mm10/mouseDevTimecourse/mouse_development_M4.facets
    singleCellColumnNames off
    html developmentTimecourseM4mm10TPM

